Time: <%= @start.strftime("%A, %B %e, %Y at %I:%M%p %Z")  %>

Location:
<%= ((@event.location_name.present? && @event.location_address.present?) && (!@event.location_address.include? @event.location_name)) ? @event.location_name + "\n" : "" %><%= @event.location_address %>

